    zhao.algorithmMagic.operands.coordinateNet.DoubleRoute2DNet.add(RouteNet<DoubleCoordinateTwo, DoubleConsanguinityRoute2D>)
    将两个网络中的每一个线路进行求和（不保证线路之间的顺序）

    Sums each line in both networks (order between lines is not guaranteed)
